<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.212123>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Leptochelia evansi. Seven Mile Beach, WA. Male dorsal (holotype), antennule (A 1), antenna (A 2), cheliped (CH), pleotelson (Plt). Scale units: 1 mm for whole animal, 0.1 mm for appendages." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/212123/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.212124>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Leptochelia evansi. Seven Mile Beach, WA. Male. Pereopods 1 – 6 (P 1 – P 6), pleopod (Pl), uropod (U). Scale units 0.1 mm for full appendages." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/212124/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

